{"tid":863083,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Fake news -【撻訂潮】上源驚現7連撻 殺定244.8萬","createTime":"2018-10-15T10:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:31:22.000Z","uid":7369,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"48463c7a397711e353f796c8dda67b9d9641f0f4","tid":863083,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"樓市大吹淡風，新盤市場更驚現小規模撻定潮。萬科(香港)屯門掃管芴新盤上源，最新錄得7宗連環撻定，連同早前2伙撻定，項目本月累積撻定個案增至9伙，最新7伙，涉及總成交價4,897萬元，殺定金額料約244.8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n萬科本月1日國慶日首輪開賣上源347伙，首日全數單位沽清，惟該批單位先錄2宗撻定，隨著進行第二輪銷售，今日再增7宗撻定個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181015/58797280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181015%2F58797280&d=SU4NCEeP1Aeco5ACME9hRJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=60a0fb6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181015%2F58797280&h=f5c1d1da\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181015/58797280</a>"},{"pid":"c652b2a0fb632dfca3776314cb022a82eff04248","tid":863083,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"屯門咁遠<br />\n當然______"},{"pid":"20e61702fdb6026326d68d8f5bb209d5fdb432ab","tid":863083,"uid":84771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"萬科樓唔計"},{"pid":"050228ed6008a68a81437f8f8bcb7641e9397f34","tid":863083,"uid":28351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c652b2a0fb632dfca3776314cb022a82eff04248","tid":863083,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"屯門咁遠<br />\n當然______"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9b9d6dd8e9a45aec415e5c95f3849a26bd097a","tid":863083,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"